lash banners and pop-ups that get in the way of browsing.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-137-2024-09-14-18-17-42/5.mp3","time_start":9.64,"time_end":13.96},{"position":6,"content":"Have you tried it on your cell phone?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-137-2024-09-14-18-17-42/6.mp3","time_start":14.21,"time_end":16.02},{"position":7,"content":"It is also mobile-optimized this time around.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-137-2024-09-14-18-17-42/7.mp3","time_start":16.02,"time_end":18.96},{"position":8,"content":"Well, I'm gonna!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-137-2024-09-14-18-17-42/8.mp3","time_start":19.48,"time_end":20.98},{"position":9,"content":"Hold on...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-137-2024-09-14-18-17-42/9.mp3","time_start":20.98,"time_end":22.12},{"position":10,"content":"How come I keep getting error messages?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-137-2024-09-14-18-17-42/10.mp3","time_start":22.27,"time_end":24.55},{"position":11,"content":"The page can only partially load.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-137-2024-09-14-18-17-42/11.mp3","time_start":24.55,"time_end":26.96},{"position":12,"content":"Good, and now it's just a blank page.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-137-2024-09-14-18-17-42/12.mp3","time_start":27.34,"time_end":30.19},{"position":13,"content":"That's weird.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-137-2024-09-14-18-17-42/13.mp3","time_start":30.89,"time_end":31.84},{"position":14,"content":"I don't have such problems.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-137-2024-09-14-18-17-42/14.mp3","time_start":31.84,"time_end":33.65},{"position":15,"content":"Did you try reloading the page?","audio_url":"https://dailydictati